{"tid":180810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雷霆17：警冚旺角色情按摩院　拉34歲女主持","createTime":"2017-03-31T07:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T11:15:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4174c90aea0f692f191b710325b306a659fd367a","tid":180810,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330210730053-0330_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170331001825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330210730053-0330_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170331001825&h=706eff82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角西洋菜南街26至36號一間樓上按摩院，表面替客人做按摩服務，實則懷疑提供色情服務。傍晚6時許，旺角警區特別職務隊派警員假扮客人放蛇，成功搗破該間「掛羊頭、賣狗肉」的色情按摩院，以涉嫌「倚靠妓女維生」及「管理賣淫場所」，拘捕一名姓戴(34歲)女主持，行動中檢獲數簿、潤滑劑、安全套、按摩床等證物。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該間按摩店經營約一年，做熟客生意，有4名本地女子駐場，按摩收198港元，加手淫服務則收400港元，當中主持拆帳150港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170330/bkn-20170330210730053-0330_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170330%2Fbkn-20170330210730053-0330_00822_001.html&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5446d74e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170330/bkn-20170330210730053-0330_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2bcbbb74f26eec14a971ea6957025721b800e71f","tid":180810,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330210730053-0330_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170331001825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330210730053-0330_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170331001825&h=706eff82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角西洋菜南街26至36號一間樓上按摩院，表面替客人做按摩服務，實則懷疑提供色情服務。傍晚6時許，旺角警區特別職務隊派警員假扮客人放蛇，成功搗破該間「掛羊頭、賣狗肉」的色情按摩院，以涉嫌「倚靠妓女維生」及「管理賣淫場所」，拘捕一名<span style=\"color: r